text: Dys synt dara XX hyda Landgemara to scireburnan ðæt inlandes.
Arest on sude yfardan<../images/tbar.gif>est andlang brotty on done herepoð nord andlang weges to scearpan brycge.
East danan andlang sledes<../images/tbar.gif>hit cinð on done weg & healfe hide on hibaldes tofte & ane hide on frysse tune on hillum twegra oxena gang.

And on on Lundby twegra oxena gang & dridde healfe hyrde on mysen forda & on stiuetune & on miclan felda II hyda land fy & lal luttringham butan anre hide & oder healf hyde on fentune & odre healf hyde on kawuda & eal<../images/tbar.gif>lid de derto gebired andlang usun ge tyfonan weorf & dacy on wuda & on weter & on felda.
